LIBRARIES USED
--------------
Bootstrap
JQuery
Hammer.js
Hammer.js JQuery Plugin


THREE INTERACTION TYPES
-----------------------

1. Hover Interaction - to reveal sliding headline panels (for Desktop)
	hover.html
	script.js

2. Scroll Interaction - to reveal sliding headline panels (for Mobile)
	scroll.html
	script.js

3. Swipe Interaction - to reveal opposite sides of the story (for Mobile)
	swipe.html
	swipe-script.js

NOTES FOR SWIPE INTERACTION
- pull window to mobile size before swiping
- swipe left/right on middle article element